ine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 1315, \"end\": 1319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"score\": 0.9812716866132364, \"rank\": 0.019085720047698446, \"text\": \"Gaza\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gaza_City\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"war\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1364}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"attack\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am clearly concerned,\\\" Anson told Sky News in an interview broadcast on April 17 to mark 100 days till the opening ceremony on July 26.\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1447, \"end\": 1452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avro_Anson\", \"score\": 0.9997381912414268, \"rank\": 0.00026187401903720383, \"text\": \"Anson\", \"types\": [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avro_Anson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Avro_Anson\"}, {\"begin\": 1458, \"end\": 1466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News\", \"score\": 0.9999999728781862, \"rank\": 2.7121699847713187e-08, \"text\": \"Sky News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_News\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interview broadcast\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1492}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1501}, {\"ngram\": \"100 days\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's one of the most important things that we have to manage from a risk perspective.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"